Industrial center & capital
Shops have all Simply & Martial equipment, and some exotic too.
Anything can be gained as Masterwork or +1
Jondi has a deal with the Mage Guild for 25% scrolls kept.
Lukas is a regular customer at the Brothel (Slooshes)
Pipa works a temp job here sometimes, making 1d4*10 gold per 2days
